{"word":"μέχρι/μέχρις","slug":"μέχρι/μέχρις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>μέχρι</el>/<el>μέχρις</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ etym.\">etym.</a> complex] a marker of limit, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gener.\">gener.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> temporally, as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prep.\">prep.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <b>until <a href='B:470 11:23'>Mt 11:23</a>; <a href='B:470 13:30'>13:30</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:470 28:15'>28:15</a>; <a href='B:490 16:16'>Lk 16:16</a>; <a href='B:510 10:30'>Ac 10:30</a>; <a href='B:510 20:7'>20:7</a>; <a href='B:520 5:14'>Ro 5:14</a>; <a href='B:650 3:6'>Hb 3:6</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>;</b> as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ conj.\">conj.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a><b>until <a href='B:480 13:30'>Mk 13:30</a>; <a href='B:550 4:19'>Gal 4:19</a>; <a href='B:560 4:13'>Eph 4:13</a></b> (without <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a>). <b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> spatially, as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prep.\">prep.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <b>as far as <a href='B:510 20:4'>Ac 20:4</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:520 15:19'>Ro 15:19</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp></b> of unusual circumstance, as <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prep.\">prep.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <b>to the point of <a href='B:620 2:9'>2 Ti 2:9</a>; <a href='B:650 12:4'>Hb 12:4</a>; <a href='B:570 2:8'>Phil 2:8</a>, <a href='B:570 2:30'>30</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:μέτωπον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"